channel.title: Plastic Molding
channel.description: I'm starting on a project that requires many custom-made plastic components. Where would I go, or who would I contact to have some prototypes of these components made? Has anyone had any experience with fabrication?

item.title: Plastic Molding
item.dc:creator: @Stupit Stu
item.description:
@Stupit wrote:

[quote=“zyle1992, post:5, topic:421040”][quote author=Stupit link=topic=523715.msg3809994#msg3809994 date=1320806443]

I made quite a few clay models by myself…

The project I’m working on will be housing a few electrical components, and I will be carrying around these plastic components (it’s for a costume).

Okay, so insulation will be needed.
[/quote]

Yes, and I may be using an RF emitter for parts of the costume, so I want to keep the amount of electrical interference to a minimum.[/quote]
I maybe able to help.
